---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About — And Still, I Lead"
  description="Ciara LaVelle writes about leadership, motherhood, ambition, and the audacity to keep going."
>
  <div class="container about-container">
    <div class="about-avatar" aria-hidden="true">CL</div>
    <span class="tag-label">About</span>
    <h1 class="about-title">Ciara LaVelle</h1>
    <div class="gold-bar"></div>

    <div class="prose about-body">
      <p>
        And Still, I Lead is not about having everything figured out. It is about choosing to show up anyway.
      </p>
      <p>
        For the moments that do not have a place. Between leadership and motherhood. Ambition and exhaustion.
      </p>
      <p>
        I am writing what it feels like to carry all of it. Not after it gets easier. Not when it is perfect. Here. In the middle of it.
      </p>
      <p>
        And still, I lead.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="contact-nudge">
      <a href="/contact" class="contact-cta">Get in touch →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-container {
    padding: 64px 0 80px;
    max-width: 600px;
  }
  .about-avatar {
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--nav-bg);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--gold);
    border: 0.5px solid var(--border);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .tag-label { display: block; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .about-title {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 34px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }
  .gold-bar {
    width: 36px;
    height: 2px;
    background: var(--gold);
    border-radius: 1px;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }
  .about-body { max-width: 540px; }
  .contact-nudge {
    margin-top: 44px;
    padding-top: 24px;
    border-top: 0.5px solid var(--border);
  }
  .contact-cta {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--gold);
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: opacity 0.15s;
  }
  .contact-cta:hover { opacity: 0.7; }
</style>
